  "title": "Radio Frequency (RF) Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Radio Frequency Engineer (RF)</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Involved in handling<strong> Radio Frequency Designs, Testing and Planning.</strong></li><li>Handle RF Specification and production transfer from prototype to production house.</li><li>Oversee assembly and ensure that products conform to technical specifications and safety regulations</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Strong in Radio Frequency Design, Testing and Design work.</strong></li><li><strong>Involved in RF specification, support and planning.</strong></li><li>Experience in handling RF work.</li><li>Proven work experience as an RF  Engineer or similar role</li><li>Degree in Electronics/Electrical/Communications Engineering </li><li>Possess Government domain (preferred)</li><li>Familiar with using RF test equipment</li><li>Singaporean Only!</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>If you feel that you have the skill-sets that we are looking for, please apply in-confidence with an updated MS Word Resume to jeline@starcareerconsulting.com</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Yong Jeline (Reg. No. R1101621)</p><p>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD (EA License: 20C0353)</p>",
